<T>__{camera moves forward to:}
<A>__{senf's desk (the old shot) meierheim is entering quickly goes through the door. he crosses now to pimenov. they talk eagerly out of earshot. but it is apparent that meierheim is, as usual, in a hurry. rohna is there too. one of the men carries a telephone stand, wrapped loosely in paper. but we know it's the telephone stand. senf comes on duty, looks around, it is apparent that he is late.}
